WEBVTT

02:07.880 --> 02:08.759
Meng Jingu,

02:09.039 --> 02:09.699
and Gong Yu,

02:09.880 --> 02:11.210
are our new classmates.

02:11.360 --> 02:13.000
Get along well with each other from now on.

02:13.000 --> 02:15.460
Let's welcome them with a round of applause.

02:17.480 --> 02:19.640
This is so unreal.

02:19.720 --> 02:21.440
He actually transferred to our class.

02:21.440 --> 02:22.240
Oh my God.

02:22.600 --> 02:24.760
Could it be because I didn't return his umbrella?

02:24.760 --> 02:25.920
Please introduce yourselves.

02:25.920 --> 02:28.040
Hello everyone, my name is Meng Jingu.

02:28.040 --> 02:29.800
I just transferred from Peiying Middle School.

02:29.800 --> 02:31.660
Please take care of me from now on.

02:31.760 --> 02:33.040
Hello everyone, I'm Gong Yu,

02:33.040 --> 02:34.079
a sports student.

02:34.160 --> 02:35.690
My grades are just average.

02:35.800 --> 02:36.800
For basketball

02:37.000 --> 02:38.520
or fights, you can call me.

02:38.680 --> 02:39.400
Gong Yu,

02:40.200 --> 02:41.520
what are you talking about?

02:41.520 --> 02:42.880
You come to school to study hard,

02:42.880 --> 02:43.720
not to fight.

02:43.960 --> 02:45.820
If you fight, see how I punish you.

02:51.040 --> 02:52.240
No fighting.

02:56.240 --> 02:57.120
Meng Jingu,

02:57.520 --> 02:58.579
go to the second row

02:58.600 --> 03:00.640
and share a desk with Xiong Yuanbao.

03:02.720 --> 03:03.680
Okay, sir.

03:08.640 --> 03:10.560
Gong Yu, go to the last row

03:10.600 --> 03:12.530
and share a desk with Wang Zhiyong.

03:12.760 --> 03:13.960
Don't cause trouble.

03:22.560 --> 03:24.520
Why don't you leave the umbrella with me,

03:24.520 --> 03:25.920
so it doesn't bother you?

03:34.800 --> 03:35.800
Wait.

03:36.800 --> 03:37.600
What's wrong?

03:37.600 --> 03:38.960
Watch out for the car.

03:54.600 --> 03:55.200
Class,

03:56.880 --> 03:58.540
open yesterday's exam paper.

04:01.960 --> 04:02.840
Meng Jingu,

04:03.160 --> 04:04.800
share with Xiong Yuanbao for now.

04:04.800 --> 04:05.800
After class,

04:06.160 --> 04:08.160
go to the office to get a new copy.

04:13.640 --> 04:14.900
What are you two doing?

04:16.120 --> 04:18.959
Gong Yu, share with Wang Zhiyong for now.

04:21.920 --> 04:24.180
Many of you got the first question wrong.

04:24.240 --> 04:25.720
Why would you choose B?

04:35.400 --> 04:36.120
Mr. Tian,

04:36.400 --> 04:38.400
I want to go back to my original seat.

04:40.000 --> 04:40.880
Mu Qingjun.

04:41.440 --> 04:43.200
You are quite a smart kid.

04:43.320 --> 04:44.560
Why can't you put that intelligence

04:44.560 --> 04:45.620
into your studies?

04:45.640 --> 04:46.680
Sleeping in class

04:46.880 --> 04:48.240
doesn't just affect you,

04:48.240 --> 04:50.120
it affects the teachers and other students.

04:50.120 --> 04:51.680
You're like a rat in a soup pot.

04:51.680 --> 04:53.540
Is it okay to ruin the whole class?

04:54.840 --> 04:57.040
If you say I'm a rat in a soup pot,

04:57.440 --> 05:00.840
what does that make the other teachers and students?

05:01.080 --> 05:02.340
They are, of course...

05:04.080 --> 05:05.940
You... are you talking back to me?

05:06.000 --> 05:06.800
Mr. Tian,

05:07.520 --> 05:08.520
I promise

05:08.760 --> 05:10.560
I'll never sleep in class again.

05:10.800 --> 05:11.720
I promise.

05:12.640 --> 05:13.970
You've made a truckload

05:14.080 --> 05:15.240
of promises to me.

05:15.440 --> 05:17.100
How many of them were sincere?

05:17.720 --> 05:18.440
Previously,

05:18.440 --> 05:19.560
when you sat with Xiong Yuanbao,

05:19.560 --> 05:21.680
you endlessly asked her for tutoring.

05:21.680 --> 05:22.610
Didn't you know?

05:22.640 --> 05:24.480
Her grades aren't much better than yours.

05:24.480 --> 05:26.120
Aren't you just holding her back?

05:26.120 --> 05:26.920
Tell you what.

05:27.280 --> 05:27.960
Don't you want to go back?

05:27.960 --> 05:28.600
Sure.

05:29.360 --> 05:30.360
In this monthly exam,

05:30.360 --> 05:31.880
if you improve your rank by 10 places,

05:31.880 --> 05:33.040
I'll let you move back.

05:33.040 --> 05:34.080
If not,

05:34.320 --> 05:36.440
you'll stay in the isolation zone and reflect on yourself.

05:36.440 --> 05:37.920
T-Ten places?

05:38.400 --> 05:39.080
What?

05:39.200 --> 05:40.060
Is that too few?

05:40.159 --> 05:41.560
N-No.

05:43.040 --> 05:45.000
L-Let me think about it.

05:45.640 --> 05:46.480
Wait, Mu Qingjun.

05:46.480 --> 05:48.320
Am I begging you?

05:49.480 --> 05:50.440
Alright.

05:50.880 --> 05:52.159
Ten places it is.

05:52.400 --> 05:53.360
Brat.

05:53.640 --> 05:54.560
Anything else?

05:55.560 --> 05:56.280
Go back.

06:09.560 --> 06:10.400
Mr. Tian.

06:10.560 --> 06:12.360
I came to pick up the test papers.

06:12.920 --> 06:13.800
Meng Jingu,

06:14.320 --> 06:15.580
with such good grades,

06:15.880 --> 06:17.410
you must set a good example.

06:17.880 --> 06:19.520
Okay, Mr. Tian.

06:24.040 --> 06:25.900
Is that the Gong Yu you mentioned?

06:26.480 --> 06:27.840
Keep your voice down.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.480
Look how happy you are.

06:32.000 --> 06:32.600
Well,

06:33.400 --> 06:34.530
what a coincidence.

06:35.040 --> 06:36.280
About last time,

06:36.480 --> 06:38.409
I haven't had a chance to thank you.

06:38.520 --> 06:39.960
No need, it was nothing.

06:40.240 --> 06:41.280
You are...

06:41.720 --> 06:43.520
I'm Tong Ruirui.

06:43.600 --> 06:46.240
Tong as in Tong Ruirui, Rui as in Tong Ruirui.

06:53.840 --> 06:56.760
Tong as in Tong Ruirui, Rui as in Tong Ruirui.

06:57.280 --> 06:58.960
It sounds like a poem.

07:00.280 --> 07:02.200
Is that what I just said?

07:03.840 --> 07:04.760
You know, life

07:04.760 --> 07:06.890
is really more dramatic than a TV show.

07:07.080 --> 07:08.760
Do you know that Meng Jingu?

07:09.000 --> 07:10.840
The one who saved me in Shanghai.

07:11.240 --> 07:12.370
The umbrella is his.

07:12.680 --> 07:14.080
Really?

07:14.680 --> 07:16.400
A city-level merit student,

07:16.920 --> 07:17.760
he saved you,

07:17.880 --> 07:19.280
and now he's your deskmate.

07:19.280 --> 07:21.400
Even novels wouldn't dare to write it like this.

07:21.400 --> 07:23.680
Right? I think it's amazing too.

07:24.960 --> 07:25.840
Do you think

07:26.400 --> 07:27.360
we both got

07:27.400 --> 07:29.840
shot by Cupid?

07:30.120 --> 07:32.400
With a shotgun, no less.

07:32.560 --> 07:33.360
That's just you.

07:33.360 --> 07:34.890
I don't have such thoughts.

07:35.720 --> 07:37.050
If it's me, then it's me.

07:37.159 --> 07:38.760
If it's me, then it's me.

07:40.440 --> 07:42.520
The exams have different difficulty levels.

07:42.520 --> 07:44.280
Advancing by exactly ten places

07:44.280 --> 07:46.120
is really hard to control.

07:46.800 --> 07:47.920
What else can I do?

07:48.440 --> 07:49.920
I can't just watch Yuanbao

07:50.120 --> 07:51.920
meet the wrong guy and go astray.

07:52.880 --> 07:54.760
Before, to make Yuanbao tutor you,

07:54.760 --> 07:57.620
you'd always score just a few points lower than her.

07:57.800 --> 07:58.960
But this time is different.

07:58.960 --> 08:01.680
You are controlling your score against the whole class.

08:01.680 --> 08:02.610
It's almost like

08:03.960 --> 08:05.440
putting a satellite into orbit.

08:05.440 --> 08:07.040
As a physics genius,

08:07.080 --> 08:08.410
if you improve too much,

08:08.840 --> 08:09.800
you'll be exposed.

08:09.800 --> 08:11.360
If you improve too little, less than ten places,

08:11.360 --> 08:13.280
won't all your efforts be in vain?

08:14.120 --> 08:15.360
This is too hard.

08:16.760 --> 08:18.760
I'm trying to figure something out.

08:20.320 --> 08:21.920
What if you let everyone know

08:21.920 --> 08:22.720
that actually

08:23.560 --> 08:25.620
your physics grades are really good?

08:25.640 --> 08:26.700
What would happen?

08:27.440 --> 08:29.400
I think Yuanbao would hate me to death.

08:29.400 --> 08:31.530
What about the college entrance exam?

08:33.919 --> 08:35.250
We still have two years.

08:35.600 --> 08:36.760
There will be a way.

08:37.679 --> 08:38.320
You

08:38.640 --> 08:40.000
must keep it a secret for me,

08:40.000 --> 08:42.080
no matter how well you knew Meng Jingu before.

08:42.080 --> 08:42.760
Got it?

08:43.480 --> 08:44.480
Don't worry, bro.

08:54.200 --> 08:54.840
What is it?

09:00.000 --> 09:01.920
This is what Ruirui waited a long time for

09:01.920 --> 09:03.520
and said she'd show me later.

09:07.320 --> 09:08.600
But what are these?

09:14.200 --> 09:16.560
Are you sure these are the most popular

09:16.680 --> 09:18.160
novels that girls like to read nowadays?

09:18.160 --> 09:19.000
Don't worry.

09:19.160 --> 09:20.720
I asked over 10 girls.

09:21.000 --> 09:22.240
I am 100 percent sure.

09:24.320 --> 09:25.120
Buying books?

09:25.360 --> 09:26.000
Yes.

09:26.360 --> 09:28.640
I want the latest girls' magazines you have here,

09:28.640 --> 09:30.760
like Hua Huo, Meng Ya,

09:30.880 --> 09:31.800
and Zhi Yin.

09:32.440 --> 09:34.770
Okay, the magazines you want are all here.

09:34.840 --> 09:35.960
Anything else?

09:38.880 --> 09:40.160
My Sunshine,

09:40.560 --> 09:41.560
My Sun...

09:45.600 --> 09:48.680
The Boss's Little Wife.

09:50.400 --> 09:52.640
Little... Wife.

09:55.080 --> 09:58.140
It's all written here anyway. Please help me find them.

09:59.240 --> 10:00.920
The handwriting is so crooked.

10:00.920 --> 10:03.600
You better read it to me and I'll find them for you.

10:03.600 --> 10:05.460
Forget it, I'll find them myself.

10:06.880 --> 10:08.520
My School Hunk,

10:08.680 --> 10:10.680
Gentle Love from the Prince?

10:10.800 --> 10:13.400
Young man, are you the one reading these?

10:14.720 --> 10:15.920
Just ring me up quickly.

10:15.920 --> 10:17.120
Stop nagging.

10:18.840 --> 10:21.440
Slow Love from Bossy Husband.

10:22.720 --> 10:24.320
For you and your bestie,

10:24.800 --> 10:26.520
I cashed in a lot of favors.

10:26.720 --> 10:27.440
Thanks.

10:28.840 --> 10:31.240
Alright, let me ask you something serious.

10:31.280 --> 10:31.880
Go ahead.

10:32.240 --> 10:35.560
What do you think of Gong Yu?

10:37.960 --> 10:39.880
Handsome, sports student.

10:39.960 --> 10:41.640
Tell me something I don't know.

10:41.640 --> 10:43.170
Transferred from Peiying.

10:43.520 --> 10:45.180
Are you doing this on purpose?

10:46.480 --> 10:48.140
The former top guy at Peiying.

10:48.440 --> 10:49.370
What did you say?

10:49.480 --> 10:50.740
Taekwondo black belt.

10:51.040 --> 10:53.440
His combat skills are about the same as mine,

10:53.440 --> 10:55.100
but his grades are just as bad.

10:56.560 --> 10:57.720
As for him,

10:58.240 --> 10:59.720
he's tough and doesn't talk much.

10:59.720 --> 11:00.920
Not easy to approach,

11:00.960 --> 11:02.560
but he should be quite loyal.

11:03.040 --> 11:05.770
Otherwise, how could he be the top guy at Peiying?

11:06.040 --> 11:06.680
By the way,

11:06.960 --> 11:08.200
tell Tong Ruirui

11:08.680 --> 11:10.080
to stay away from Gong Yu.

11:10.360 --> 11:11.120
A guy like Gong Yu

11:11.120 --> 11:14.040
is not someone an innocent girl like her should mess with.

11:14.040 --> 11:15.280
What are you talking about?

11:15.280 --> 11:16.810
Ruirui didn't ask me to ask.

11:16.840 --> 11:17.640
Come on.

11:17.800 --> 11:18.930
Look at Tong Ruirui,

11:18.960 --> 11:20.880
she can't take her eyes off him.

11:23.360 --> 11:24.360
You noticed?

11:24.760 --> 11:25.760
What do you think?

11:31.160 --> 11:31.800
Ghost!

11:32.640 --> 11:33.280
Mu Qingjun!

11:33.280 --> 11:33.960
Come catch me!

11:33.960 --> 11:35.890
If you catch me, I'll buy you a cake.

11:36.720 --> 11:37.920
Stop right there.

11:39.440 --> 11:40.640
Still running!

11:41.600 --> 11:43.760
I have a cousin who goes to Peiying.

11:43.840 --> 11:44.880
He knows Gong Yu.

11:45.360 --> 11:48.120
I heard that when he was at Peiying,

11:48.240 --> 11:49.640
he had a bad reputation.

11:50.240 --> 11:51.320
A bad reputation?

11:51.840 --> 11:53.040
I heard he stole money

11:53.120 --> 11:54.280
and even hit girls.

11:54.840 --> 11:56.720
Really? No way.

11:57.200 --> 11:58.480
That's the rumor.

11:58.560 --> 12:00.000
Who knows if it's true?

12:00.480 --> 12:03.000
It seems you can't judge a book by its cover.

12:03.160 --> 12:04.200
How could this be?

12:06.120 --> 12:07.800
Hitting girls?

12:13.360 --> 12:14.680
Stay away from Gong Yu.

12:15.000 --> 12:15.720
Someone like Gong Yu

12:15.720 --> 12:17.960
is not someone a delicate girl like her can mess with.

12:17.960 --> 12:19.320
No, no.

12:23.880 --> 12:25.200
Yuanbao, go back to your seat.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.530
Class is about to start.

12:30.920 --> 12:32.560
Class, next week

12:32.680 --> 12:34.640
is our first monthly exam of this semester.

12:34.640 --> 12:36.480
You all know where you ranked

12:36.560 --> 12:38.160
in our class last semester, right?

12:38.160 --> 12:39.560
I hope this semester,

12:39.800 --> 12:41.280
you can work hard and endure hardships.

12:41.280 --> 12:42.200
As the saying goes,

12:42.200 --> 12:43.760
many hands make light work.

12:43.880 --> 12:44.800
If each of you

12:44.920 --> 12:46.120
takes a small step forward,

12:46.120 --> 12:47.480
it will be a giant leap

12:47.640 --> 12:48.920
for our class.

12:49.240 --> 12:50.000
I hope

12:50.160 --> 12:51.040
our class this semester

12:51.040 --> 12:52.360
can make it into the top six.

12:52.360 --> 12:53.160
I still

12:53.440 --> 12:54.770
have confidence in you.

12:56.840 --> 12:57.570
Who laughed?

12:59.520 --> 13:00.440
Ignorant.

13:01.560 --> 13:02.490
Holding us back.

13:02.760 --> 13:03.640
Who laughed?

13:04.600 --> 13:05.600
Have you no shame?

13:06.240 --> 13:08.760
You are literally the worst class I've ever taught.

13:08.760 --> 13:10.680
Especially with you black sheep.

13:11.200 --> 13:12.480
The bottom few in this monthly exam

13:12.480 --> 13:13.320
must bring your parents.

13:13.320 --> 13:15.050
I will talk to them personally.

13:16.080 --> 13:17.410
To improve your grades,

13:17.600 --> 13:19.360
the other teachers and I have decided

13:19.360 --> 13:21.120
to form mutual study groups.

13:21.320 --> 13:23.680
I'll read the list now.

13:24.160 --> 13:24.960
For Group 1,

13:25.320 --> 13:26.160
the leaders

13:26.440 --> 13:28.160
are Xing Yaqi and Meng Jingu.

13:28.240 --> 13:30.480
The members are Xiong Yuanbao,

13:30.840 --> 13:31.640
Tong Ruirui,

13:31.960 --> 13:32.840
Shang Ningyu,

13:33.440 --> 13:34.300
and Mu Qingyun.

13:34.360 --> 13:35.200
Zhang Dongbo.

13:36.520 --> 13:38.680
Group Two. Leader, Qiao Yan.

13:39.400 --> 13:40.960
Member, Gong Yu.

13:41.080 --> 13:43.480
Group Four. Leader, Zhou Mengzhi.

13:44.080 --> 13:44.880
Members,

13:45.440 --> 13:46.240
Wang Zhiyong,

13:46.720 --> 13:47.520
Zhang Ming.

13:50.280 --> 13:51.080
Ruirui.

13:51.800 --> 13:53.440
Ruirui, where have you been?

13:53.560 --> 13:54.600
I've been looking for you.

13:54.600 --> 13:55.960
I have something to tell you.

13:55.960 --> 13:58.840
Yuanbao, I have something to tell you too.

13:59.560 --> 14:00.720
What is it?

14:02.320 --> 14:05.720
I just applied to Mr. Tian.

14:06.400 --> 14:09.040
I'm going to study in Group Two.

14:11.000 --> 14:12.400
For Gong Yu?

14:14.200 --> 14:15.520
No, Ruirui.

14:15.840 --> 14:17.880
I don't want you to get hurt.

14:18.200 --> 14:19.560
Get hurt?

14:20.440 --> 14:21.720
What do you mean?

14:22.360 --> 14:24.880
Actually, Gong Yu is not who you think he is.

14:25.200 --> 14:27.130
Don't be fooled by his appearance.

14:28.640 --> 14:30.600
Did Qingjun tell you something?

14:30.840 --> 14:31.960
No.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.800
I was in the restroom

14:35.160 --> 14:37.290
and heard two girls talking about him.

14:37.640 --> 14:39.880
What did they say?

14:40.840 --> 14:41.720
They said

14:42.840 --> 14:44.560
when Gong Yu was at Peiying,

14:45.800 --> 14:47.720
he not only stole money

14:48.560 --> 14:49.760
but also hit girls.

14:50.480 --> 14:51.740
Xiong Yuanbao, right?

14:57.880 --> 14:59.600
Do you know how terrible it is to talk behind someone's back

14:59.600 --> 15:01.520
and spread rumors?

15:02.960 --> 15:04.000
You think just because you're a girl,

15:04.000 --> 15:05.320
I won't touch you?

15:05.480 --> 15:06.740
I dare you to touch her.

15:11.480 --> 15:12.940
It's a misunderstanding.

15:14.880 --> 15:16.160
Go.

15:16.680 --> 15:17.360
Go.

15:17.760 --> 15:18.920
Sorry.

15:19.080 --> 15:19.880
Sorry.

15:19.960 --> 15:20.600
Gong Yu.

15:23.200 --> 15:24.560
I think you're great.

15:24.920 --> 15:26.960
You're not like what they say.

15:29.880 --> 15:30.920
Ruirui, let's go.

15:36.040 --> 15:37.360
I will hit girls.

15:38.080 --> 15:39.810
Your name is Mu Qingjun, right?

15:40.000 --> 15:41.530
Keep an eye on her yourself.

15:49.160 --> 15:51.120
Ruirui, I'm sorry.

15:51.520 --> 15:52.800
I only heard about it.

15:52.840 --> 15:54.600
It's for your own good, Ruirui.

15:57.680 --> 15:58.400
Ruirui.

16:00.120 --> 16:01.880
Listen to me, Ruirui.

16:15.040 --> 16:15.760
Ruirui.

16:16.400 --> 16:18.000
What I told you today,

16:18.160 --> 16:20.080
I wasn't trying to badmouth him.

16:20.360 --> 16:22.040
I'm genuinely worried about you.

16:22.040 --> 16:23.160
Don't get me wrong.

16:38.040 --> 16:38.720
Yuanbao.

16:39.400 --> 16:41.280
I know you're looking out for me,

16:41.760 --> 16:44.320
but I still can't believe

16:44.480 --> 16:46.520
that someone who'd protect a strange girl

16:46.520 --> 16:47.920
would do such things.

16:48.280 --> 16:49.120
I think

16:49.520 --> 16:51.400
I should get to know him better.

16:51.800 --> 16:54.120
He's probably not what he seems to be.

16:54.840 --> 16:55.900
As for this matter,

16:56.360 --> 16:57.960
please don't interfere anymore.

16:57.960 --> 16:58.640
Thank you.

17:00.400 --> 17:02.760
Oh no. She's obsessed.

17:03.360 --> 17:06.040
She's putting me on the opposing side.

17:26.160 --> 17:28.600
Sorry, I zoned out again.

17:28.960 --> 17:32.000
Yuanbao, why is Ruirui in Group Two?

17:34.280 --> 17:35.080
What's wrong?

17:35.440 --> 17:36.440
Are you okay?

17:37.320 --> 17:38.160
I'm fine.

17:39.640 --> 17:41.440
In ancient times, scholars always had teachers.

17:41.440 --> 17:44.000
A teacher is one who propagates doctrines, imparts professional knowledge, and resolves doubts.

17:44.000 --> 17:45.320
Since people are not born with knowledge,

17:45.320 --> 17:46.400
who can be without doubts?

17:46.400 --> 17:48.360
If one has doubts but does not learn from a teacher, their doubts

17:48.360 --> 17:49.360
will never be resolved.

17:49.360 --> 17:50.560
For those born before me,

17:50.560 --> 17:52.720
they naturally learned the truth before me,

17:52.720 --> 17:54.450
so I follow them as my teachers.

17:54.840 --> 17:55.760
Well...

17:55.960 --> 17:58.480
For those born after me,

17:58.720 --> 18:00.520
and I follow,

18:00.840 --> 18:02.440
I follow them as my teachers.

18:04.960 --> 18:06.000
I learn the truth,

18:06.440 --> 18:09.600
so why should I care if they were born before or after me?

18:12.200 --> 18:13.000
Where are we?

18:18.200 --> 18:19.160
I don't know.

18:19.480 --> 18:23.720
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six...

18:23.880 --> 18:27.680
Five, four, three, two, one.

18:27.800 --> 18:33.600
Sing, sing, sing.

18:33.760 --> 18:35.720
Mu Qingyun, can I join your group?

18:38.760 --> 18:39.600
Sure.

18:39.800 --> 18:42.200
What do you want to sing? I'll sing with you.

18:43.720 --> 18:44.850
Let's sing that one.

18:45.560 --> 18:48.840
Every time,

18:48.960 --> 18:52.000
I stay strong through wandering and loneliness.

18:52.160 --> 18:58.080
Every time, even when hurt, I don't shed a tear.

18:58.280 --> 19:04.640
I know I've always had a pair of invisible wings.

19:04.840 --> 19:06.560
Fly with me,

19:06.720 --> 19:09.880
past the despair.

19:11.000 --> 19:12.760
Not bad. You have talent.

19:12.800 --> 19:15.760
Didn't they almost get into a fight a few days ago?

19:15.840 --> 19:18.120
Why are they suddenly singing together now?

19:18.120 --> 19:19.000
At this moment,

19:19.120 --> 19:21.160
I just want to ask the scriptwriter of my life,

19:21.160 --> 19:22.160
could the things happening to me

19:22.160 --> 19:23.620
be any more melodramatic?

19:23.760 --> 19:24.820
Let's go, Qingjun.

19:28.480 --> 19:29.560
Let's go, Qingjun.

19:30.400 --> 19:31.260
School is over.

19:32.000 --> 19:33.000
Ruirui, bye-bye.

19:33.680 --> 19:34.160
Bye-bye.

19:34.160 --> 19:35.160
Yuanbao, I'm leaving.

19:35.160 --> 19:35.920
Bye-bye.

19:42.560 --> 19:43.490
Ruirui, Ruirui.

19:43.560 --> 19:44.280
Ruirui.

19:45.640 --> 19:47.600
Can you just listen to my advice?

19:47.840 --> 19:48.680
Yuanbao.

19:49.520 --> 19:51.650
You don't have to persuade me anymore.

19:51.680 --> 19:53.160
I know what I want to do.

20:04.600 --> 20:05.320
Oh no.

20:05.480 --> 20:06.540
Ruirui is missing.

20:25.520 --> 20:26.160
Gong Yu.

20:28.120 --> 20:28.840
Um...

20:29.880 --> 20:31.200
You saved me last time.

20:31.520 --> 20:33.780
I haven't had the chance to thank you yet.

20:34.520 --> 20:35.320
So,

20:36.600 --> 20:37.520
this is for you.

20:51.320 --> 20:53.000
You've been here for so many days,

20:53.000 --> 20:54.930
and don't really have any friends.

20:55.040 --> 20:56.240
So I was wondering...

20:57.320 --> 20:59.080
Can I be your friend?

20:59.640 --> 21:01.170
I understand what you mean.

21:01.680 --> 21:02.800
But,

21:03.000 --> 21:05.600
I don't really like making friends with girls.

21:06.000 --> 21:08.120
I appreciate the thought.

21:09.080 --> 21:10.360
As for this scarf,

21:10.440 --> 21:11.900
I don't like black either.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.890
You should give it to someone else.

21:35.600 --> 21:36.400
Ruirui.

21:36.920 --> 21:37.760
Ruirui.

21:38.160 --> 21:39.020
I'm right here.

21:39.160 --> 21:41.200
Wait for me there. Don't leave.

21:54.040 --> 21:55.320
Why are you here?

21:55.520 --> 21:57.120
You're asking me why I'm here?

21:57.120 --> 21:58.320
Why are you here?

21:58.760 --> 22:00.960
I finally found you. I was worried sick.

22:03.360 --> 22:04.420
Why are you crying?

22:05.080 --> 22:06.740
What's wrong? What happened?

22:06.800 --> 22:08.060
Did someone bully you?

22:10.520 --> 22:11.440
I'm fine.

22:12.080 --> 22:14.800
Didn't you say you'd take me to check out cram schools?

22:14.800 --> 22:16.880
I waited for you for a long time, but you didn't show up.

22:16.880 --> 22:18.720
I called you, but you didn't answer.

22:18.720 --> 22:20.000
So I called Yuanbao.

22:20.280 --> 22:21.960
Yuanbao called your home.

22:22.080 --> 22:24.210
And we found out you weren't even home.

22:24.280 --> 22:26.080
Everyone was so worried.

22:26.160 --> 22:27.160
We all came out looking for you.

22:27.160 --> 22:29.080
We were afraid something had happened.

22:29.080 --> 22:30.480
Yuanbao came out too?

22:31.200 --> 22:32.440
My phone died.

22:32.520 --> 22:34.850
I didn't know you guys were looking for me.

22:35.120 --> 22:36.520
I made you worry.

22:36.720 --> 22:37.640
I'm sorry.

22:38.280 --> 22:38.960
Alright.

22:39.640 --> 22:42.170
As long as you're okay, nothing else matters.

22:42.200 --> 22:43.680
Let's go. I'll take you home.

22:43.680 --> 22:45.560
You should tell Yuanbao first.

22:45.680 --> 22:46.920
Don't let her worry.

22:47.040 --> 22:47.880
Right.

22:48.600 --> 22:50.660
Yuanbao was just crying out of worry.

22:50.720 --> 22:53.040
She cried out of worry?

22:53.320 --> 22:54.240
Of course.

22:54.280 --> 22:56.210
Aren't you two as close as sisters?

22:59.920 --> 23:00.520
Yuanbao.

23:00.720 --> 23:02.080
I found it.

23:17.040 --> 23:18.080
Here you go.

23:26.720 --> 23:29.160
Sisters are the best.

23:30.440 --> 23:31.760
What's wrong, Ruirui?

23:32.200 --> 23:33.200
What happened?

23:33.960 --> 23:35.680
Last night,

23:36.160 --> 23:38.960
I went to tell Gong Yu

23:39.200 --> 23:41.560
that I wanted to be friends,

23:42.520 --> 23:44.080
but I was rejected.

23:44.680 --> 23:45.960
I told you

23:46.040 --> 23:47.840
he doesn't have good character.

23:47.880 --> 23:48.680
Why did you...

23:49.480 --> 23:50.440
All right.

23:50.800 --> 23:52.800
Even if his character isn't bad,

23:53.240 --> 23:54.600
and we misunderstood him,

23:54.600 --> 23:55.320
but

23:55.520 --> 23:56.760
why would he refuse

23:56.840 --> 23:58.100
to be friends with you?

23:58.560 --> 23:59.690
What was his reason?

24:00.800 --> 24:01.480
He said

24:01.960 --> 24:04.290
he doesn't like being friends with girls.

24:04.640 --> 24:06.040
You're missing the point.

24:06.040 --> 24:07.240
What do you mean?

24:07.960 --> 24:10.360
I feel like Gong Yu joined our group

24:10.560 --> 24:11.680
not because of you,

24:12.080 --> 24:13.410
but for something else.

24:14.680 --> 24:15.640
Something else?

24:17.240 --> 24:18.800
He came for Mu Qingjun.

24:21.000 --> 24:21.800
Right.

24:22.360 --> 24:24.760
They were at each other's throats the other day

24:24.760 --> 24:26.620
and almost fought because of you.

24:27.000 --> 24:28.130
What a coincidence.

24:28.480 --> 24:29.880
Let me ask you something.

24:29.960 --> 24:31.160
Did you see Mutou?

24:31.360 --> 24:32.840
I just saw Qingyun

24:32.880 --> 24:34.320
and Gong Yu

24:34.400 --> 24:35.400
going to the roof.

24:35.800 --> 24:37.240
The roof?

24:37.560 --> 24:38.090
Let's go.

24:38.160 --> 24:38.960
Let's go.

24:39.240 --> 24:39.800
Hurry up.

24:39.880 --> 24:40.480
Follow me.

24:45.920 --> 24:47.280
Since you are in Zhicheng,

24:47.280 --> 24:48.940
I will protect you from now on.

24:49.560 --> 24:50.880
Okay, I'll rely on you.

24:59.000 --> 24:59.800
Yuanbao,

25:00.440 --> 25:01.760
how did they

25:02.640 --> 25:04.760
become so close?

25:17.680 --> 25:18.880
What are you reading?

25:19.080 --> 25:20.920
Studying so hard?

25:26.680 --> 25:27.640
What are you writing?

25:27.640 --> 25:29.300
Questions from someone else.

25:29.640 --> 25:30.600
Oh my god.

25:30.880 --> 25:33.010
They are actually studying together.

25:35.040 --> 25:37.320
Not even this serious with me.

25:41.040 --> 25:41.760
No.

25:42.240 --> 25:43.360
I have to find a way.

25:44.680 --> 25:45.920
I can't tell Ruirui.

25:58.120 --> 25:58.920
Gamma.

25:59.440 --> 26:01.960
Him again. Interesting.

26:03.480 --> 26:04.800
For the sharks,

26:04.800 --> 26:06.800
what a feast of a day this is.

26:06.840 --> 26:08.840
There's more food than they can eat.

26:08.840 --> 26:09.700
Don't eat this.

26:10.200 --> 26:11.360
You go get a new one.

26:16.320 --> 26:18.680
Grandma, didn't I tell you?

26:18.720 --> 26:21.180
Eating expired food will give you diarrhea.

26:22.080 --> 26:23.480
Today is the last day.

26:23.520 --> 26:25.000
Only after tonight

26:25.080 --> 26:26.160
will it be expired.

26:26.440 --> 26:28.000
We can't waste food.

26:28.360 --> 26:29.960
I'll eat it. You get a new one.

26:34.200 --> 26:35.330
Then I'll eat it too.

26:36.080 --> 26:37.810
It's faster if we eat together.

26:39.880 --> 26:41.240
The monthly exams are coming up soon, right?

26:41.240 --> 26:42.680
The shark doesn't care.

26:42.960 --> 26:43.960
There's still a lot of food.

26:43.960 --> 26:45.240
You need to be sensible

26:45.520 --> 26:46.680
and study hard.

26:46.960 --> 26:47.960
Ask your teachers

26:48.200 --> 26:51.000
and good classmates for more advice.

26:53.080 --> 26:53.960
Besides,

26:54.240 --> 26:56.440
Qingyun's family has helped us so much.

26:56.760 --> 26:58.800
You should help him out too.

26:59.880 --> 27:01.200
Don't worry, Grandma.

27:02.520 --> 27:04.850
I will definitely supervise and push him.

27:06.880 --> 27:07.920
Good kid.

27:27.320 --> 27:29.960
If there are three long options and one short option, choose the shortest one.

27:29.960 --> 27:33.840
If there are three short options and one long option, choose the longest one.

27:33.840 --> 27:36.040
The answer to this question should be C.

27:42.720 --> 27:44.780
This question is quite interesting.

27:54.280 --> 27:55.920
Brother, please help me.

28:04.440 --> 28:05.040
Come.

28:05.560 --> 28:07.620
Let's see how you guys did on the exam.

28:15.600 --> 28:17.480
I will work harder next time.

28:17.640 --> 28:19.280
I won't get so many questions wrong again.

28:19.280 --> 28:20.240
Xiong Yuanbao.

28:20.720 --> 28:23.380
You're tenth from the bottom and still talking?

28:23.400 --> 28:24.400
Go stand at the back.

28:24.400 --> 28:25.040
Me?

28:25.440 --> 28:26.840
What are you laughing at?

28:27.880 --> 28:29.320
The bottom ten students in this monthly exam,

28:29.320 --> 28:31.120
go stand at the back and reflect.

28:31.840 --> 28:33.570
You guys are really something.

28:34.400 --> 28:36.000
Class One surpassed us again.

28:36.000 --> 28:37.600
You've completely embarrassed me.

28:37.600 --> 28:39.560
The bottom ten must bring their parents.

28:39.560 --> 28:41.490
We're in this together, brothers.

28:41.720 --> 28:42.720
Shang Ningyu,

28:42.920 --> 28:45.680
you're at the bottom and still have the nerve to talk?

28:45.680 --> 28:46.800
Whenever you guys get together,

28:46.800 --> 28:48.080
you just can't keep your mouths shut.

28:48.080 --> 28:50.410
Truly a few bad apples spoiling the bunch.

28:52.720 --> 28:54.440
Mu Qingyun totally crushed it.

28:54.440 --> 28:56.100
I'm sure everyone has seen it.

28:56.520 --> 28:58.920
This time, I must praise Mu Qingyun.

29:00.600 --> 29:01.320
Where is he?

29:02.080 --> 29:03.280
Sir, he

29:03.360 --> 29:04.520
said he

29:05.240 --> 29:06.370
went to get some sun.

29:06.640 --> 29:08.200
What's everyone laughing at?

29:08.200 --> 29:10.400
Although Mu Qingyun usually goofs off,

29:10.480 --> 29:11.610
he moved up 13 places

29:11.720 --> 29:12.920
in this monthly exam,

29:13.120 --> 29:15.280
and he even solved the last major physics question.

29:15.280 --> 29:16.040
Look at yourselves,

29:16.040 --> 29:17.200
especially you guys.

29:17.200 --> 29:19.000
Mr. Tian, you must be mistaken.

29:19.200 --> 29:20.440
Yeah, Mr. Tian.

29:20.520 --> 29:22.560
That's an out-of-syllabus physics question.

29:22.560 --> 29:24.320
Could Mu Qingyun have cheated?

29:24.920 --> 29:26.280
Don't slander people.

29:26.440 --> 29:28.160
How is that slander?

29:28.440 --> 29:29.640
During the exam,

29:29.760 --> 29:32.240
Mu Qingyun sat right in front of Meng Jingu.

29:32.440 --> 29:34.720
And they were the only two who got it right.

29:34.720 --> 29:36.000
That's very strange.

29:38.120 --> 29:39.320
The answering steps.

29:40.120 --> 29:41.850
They are indeed quite similar.

29:43.280 --> 29:44.040
Impossible.

29:44.640 --> 29:46.200
Mu Qingyun would not cheat.

29:48.920 --> 29:50.450
If he really wanted to cheat

29:50.600 --> 29:52.560
and cared that much about his grades,

29:52.560 --> 29:54.890
he wouldn't rank at the bottom every time.

29:55.280 --> 29:58.120
You only see the side of him that skips classes, fights,

29:58.120 --> 29:59.280
and plays games.

30:00.040 --> 30:01.200
But who knows that

30:01.280 --> 30:02.560
before the exam,

30:02.920 --> 30:05.450
he studied in the library late into the night?

30:06.200 --> 30:08.400
Maybe he has done this question before.

30:08.640 --> 30:09.560
Or maybe

30:10.280 --> 30:11.520
he is just smart.

30:11.880 --> 30:13.600
But he could never have cheated.

30:13.600 --> 30:15.080
I swear on my honor,

30:15.120 --> 30:16.720
he is not that kind of person.

30:17.160 --> 30:18.160
You have no proof.

30:18.240 --> 30:19.880
How can you slander him like this?

30:19.880 --> 30:22.040
Exactly. Mu Qingyun didn't cheat.

30:22.120 --> 30:23.180
I trust my brother.

30:23.440 --> 30:24.160
I trust him too.

30:24.160 --> 30:24.690
Exactly.

30:24.720 --> 30:26.120
What's the use of your trust?

30:26.120 --> 30:27.640
Show us the proof.

30:27.840 --> 30:29.880
Who has proof that he didn't cheat?

30:29.920 --> 30:30.800
If you say so,

30:30.840 --> 30:32.720
show us the proof that he cheated.

30:33.160 --> 30:35.480
His usual test scores are the proof.

30:35.560 --> 30:36.920
We all know that.

30:37.400 --> 30:39.160
Mutou wouldn't cheat.

30:39.600 --> 30:41.060
He wouldn't stoop to that.

30:41.400 --> 30:42.640
I know his character.

30:42.800 --> 30:44.240
To slander him without proof,

30:44.240 --> 30:45.600
isn't it a bit too much?

30:46.280 --> 30:47.680
It's my first time seeing

30:47.960 --> 30:48.760
someone

30:49.280 --> 30:50.440
so brave,

30:51.000 --> 30:53.880
taking another person's side without asking questions.

30:53.880 --> 30:55.360
This reckless courage

30:55.480 --> 30:56.760
and unwavering faith

30:57.200 --> 30:59.720
make her shine brightly

30:59.960 --> 31:01.720
and look especially cute right now.

31:01.720 --> 31:03.120
All right, stop arguing.

31:04.360 --> 31:05.280
Meng Jingu.

31:06.080 --> 31:07.010
During the exam,

31:07.400 --> 31:09.000
Mu Qingjun was sitting right in front of you.

31:09.000 --> 31:10.160
Whether he cheated or not,

31:10.160 --> 31:11.360
you must know best.

31:20.760 --> 31:22.160
Mr. Tian, Mu Qingjun...

31:22.240 --> 31:23.000
Reporting.

31:25.160 --> 31:26.420
You finally showed up.

31:26.760 --> 31:28.560
I should get a note from the principal

31:28.560 --> 31:29.560
and have you expelled.

31:29.560 --> 31:32.320
Sir, I promise I won't be late next time.

31:34.760 --> 31:36.880
Perfect timing. We were just discussing your exam.

31:36.880 --> 31:39.120
Sir, I heard everything at the door.

31:42.320 --> 31:44.560
Thank you all for your trust,

31:45.000 --> 31:46.600
but I have to disappoint you.

31:47.680 --> 31:49.080
I did copy Meng's paper.

31:58.320 --> 31:59.880
It really is his handwriting.
